  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLATLAND - Vol. 2</strong> is a fast-paced hardcore platformer featuring hand-crafted levels and Lightning-fast respawns. Help Square cross the most dangerous part of Flatland: the flooded wells.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls are simple and accessible but with several layers of depth to master; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of items to collect and new game modes to unlock; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lightning-fast respawns keep you in the flow even in more difficult levels; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging, fast, and fun gameplay. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run, jump, die, learn, repeat.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FLATLAND - Vol. 2</strong> is a fast-paced hardcore platformer featuring hand-crafted levels and Lightning-fast respawns. Help Square cross the most dangerous part of Flatland: the flooded wells.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controls are simple and accessible but with several layers of depth to master; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of items to collect and new game modes to unlock; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lightning-fast respawns keep you in the flow even in more difficult levels; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging, fast, and fun gameplay. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run, jump, die, learn, repeat.</strong></p>",
